So you're gonna do a solo piece.
Somewhere hot.

00:07.107 --> 00:09.174
Apparently, there was an incident
at the car wash last night.

00:09.209 --> 00:11.043
I have to head in.
Would you look at that?

00:12.112 --> 00:13.112
Good evening, ladies.

00:13.146 --> 00:14.880
Which baby are we
visiting tonight?

00:14.915 --> 00:16.148
Craig, it's Kathryn.

00:16.181 --> 00:17.950
I think I might have
figured out

00:17.984 --> 00:20.085
who Angelo's source
at the hospital is.

00:20.120 --> 00:21.820
<i>Good evening,</i>
<i>ladies and gentlemen.</i>

